{"tid":424740,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"譚俊彥傷手冇得抱Big爆朱晨麗","createTime":"2017-10-05T04:50:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-05T12:04:17.000Z","uid":81228,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"849dbf9b232ef37f9e1724f7f5b5d871350d6cca","tid":424740,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T04:50:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171005/photo/bkn-20171005000503436-1005_00862_001_01b.jpg?20171005055445\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20171005%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171005000503436-1005_00862_001_01b.jpg%3F20171005055445&h=544d4ddd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n譚俊彥整傷手照開工，真係要小心。<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171005/photo/bkn-20171005000503436-1005_00862_001_02b.jpg?20171005055445\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20171005%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171005000503436-1005_00862_001_02b.jpg%3F20171005055445&h=0c53e4f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n譚俊彥被璃鎅傷手要縫18針。<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171005/photo/bkn-20171005000503436-1005_00862_001_03b.jpg?20171005055445\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20171005%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171005000503436-1005_00862_001_03b.jpg%3F20171005055445&h=8d7681d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n譚俊彥戴上透明手套以防感染。<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171005/photo/bkn-20171005000503436-1005_00862_001_04b.jpg?20171005055445\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20171005%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171005000503436-1005_00862_001_04b.jpg%3F20171005055445&h=bc6eb6a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n慘慘豬啦！<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171005/photo/bkn-20171005000503436-1005_00862_001_05b.jpg?20171005055445\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20171005%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171005000503436-1005_00862_001_05b.jpg%3F20171005055445&h=3d4bd382&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n相當認真！<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171005/photo/bkn-20171005000503436-1005_00862_001_06b.jpg?20171005055445\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20171005%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171005000503436-1005_00862_001_06b.jpg%3F20171005055445&h=65557aaa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好迷人呀！<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171005/photo/bkn-20171005000503436-1005_00862_001_07b.jpg?20171005055445\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20171005%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171005000503436-1005_00862_001_07b.jpg%3F20171005055445&h=e4701f8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n朱晨麗對譚俊彥受傷感到心痛。<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171005/photo/bkn-20171005000503436-1005_00862_001_08b.jpg?20171005055445\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20171005%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171005000503436-1005_00862_001_08b.jpg%3F20171005055445&h=07651444&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n朱晨麗讚譚俊彥係硬漢子。<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171005/photo/bkn-20171005000503436-1005_00862_001_09b.jpg?20171005055445\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20171005%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171005000503436-1005_00862_001_09b.jpg%3F20171005055445&h=86407163&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n朱晨麗想幫譚俊彥着襪。<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171005/photo/bkn-20171005000503436-1005_00862_001_10b.jpg?20171005055445\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20171005%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171005000503436-1005_00862_001_10b.jpg%3F20171005055445&h=70e3b8f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n譚俊彥話唔使啦！<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171005/photo/bkn-20171005000503436-1005_00862_001_11b.jpg?20171005055445\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20171005%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171005000503436-1005_00862_001_11b.jpg%3F20171005055445&h=f1c6ddd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n朱晨麗好有心！<br />\n<br />\n藝人譚俊彥（Shaun）拍攝無綫劇《特技人》碌落山戲時，被玻璃鎅傷手要縫18針，他仍帶傷與着上貼身Tee大晒34D「Big爆」上圍的朱晨麗，在堅尼地城繼續拍攝，Shaun左手手掌兩處傷口貼上膠布，並戴上透明手套以防感染。他透露一早就開工，幸好只是文戲，但有幕要抱起朱晨麗（朱朱）則要替身代勞，問到何以不停工休息？他說：「其實我受傷之後第一句係對唔住，我唔想阻大家拍攝時間，朱朱之後又要入另一套劇，所以今日我係唔會休息，都係皮外傷啫！（傷口仲有冇好痛？）縫針唔算痛，係打麻醉針嗰陣好痛，同埋要翻開傷口睇吓仲有冇玻璃碎，依家冇咩事喇！大場面已經拍完，但仲有由架車跌落地嘅戲，我仲有隻右手，冇問題！」<br />\n<br />\n<strong>跟太太講對不起</strong><br />\n<br />\nShaun表示最想跟太太說句對不起：「喺醫院都冇咩嘢，返到屋企佢見到我成身瘀晒，就開始喊，真係嚇親佢！對唔住！」他指父親狄龍及母親陶敏明都清楚拍動作戲受傷在所難免，狄龍當年更受過更重傷，Shaun說：「我係佢哋個仔，點都心痛，但知道演員係咁，趁後生仲可以衝吓。（所以冇後悔親身上陣？）拍出嚟好靚，係值得嘅，係唔好意思令大家擔心。（從影以來最重傷呢次？）唔係，試過甩骹。（就嚟煞科有冇得休息？）月中煞科，應該有得抖一個月，但依家專心工作埋佢先。」<br />\n<br />\n<strong>朱晨麗讚硬漢子</strong><br />\n<br />\n朱晨麗則為拍檔Shaun受傷大感心痛，大讚對方是硬漢子，問有否照顧對方？她說：「佢咩都自己嚟，佢受傷好多嘢唔方便，例如着襪，我哋想幫佢，佢都話唔使，真係好堅強。」Shaun笑言多數自己照顧別人，不習慣被人照顧。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171005/bkn-20171005000503436-1005_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20171005%2Fbkn-20171005000503436-1005_00862_001.html&d=qm%2FEjCb%2BruC%2FKbOXS6utqMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=9301237b\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171005/bkn-20171005000503436-1005_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"52aeb51ee3c5d8305ed560b19d315b691cfd0811","tid":424740,"uid":33907,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T04:54:53.000Z","msg":"邊撚個"},{"pid":"a5c2aa34a2b4567721385a80dc2db33d6e0d57ed","tid":424740,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T04:55:52.000Z","msg":"二打六放開個女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkg